CustomProperties.Name: TabSelected
CustomProperties.Tooltip: Action based on which tab is selected

CustomProperties.Name: DefaultTab
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property for setting the default tab that should be selected.

CustomProperties.Name: TabTemplateSize
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to adjust the overall width of the tabs when labels are being shown.

CustomProperties.Name: Filled
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to set the filled property.

CustomProperties.Name: PrimaryOrange
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to set the primary color.

CustomProperties.Name: IconsOnly
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to toggle icons as main identifiers.

CustomProperties.Name: TabsWidth
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property for the tabs width.

Rules.InvariantScript: If('Tabs (Icons and Labels)'.Filled = true, ColorValue("#F3F3F3"), RGBA(0,0,0,0))
LookUp('Tabs (Icons and Labels)'.TabItems, Tab_Name = 'Tabs (Icons and Labels)'.DefaultTab)
If(ThisItem.IsSelected, If('Tabs (Icons and Labels)'.PrimaryOrange = true, ColorValue("#D04A02"), ColorValue("#415385")), RGBA(0,0,0,0))
If('Tabs (Icons and Labels)'.IconsOnly = true, false, true)
If('Tabs (Icons and Labels)'.Filled = true, If(ThisItem.IsSelected, Self.Fill, ColorValue("#E8E8E8")), RGBA(0,0,0,0))
If('Tabs (Icons and Labels)'.IconsOnly = true, Parent.TemplateWidth/2 - Self.Width/2, 10)
If(ThisItem.IsSelected, If('Tabs (Icons and Labels)'.PrimaryOrange = true, ColorValue("#D04A02"), ColorValue("#415385")), RGBA(0,0,0,0))
